users

Class Subscriber

  • java.lang.Object
    • users.Subscriber

  • public class Subscriber
extends java.lang.Object
    Confidence is the data and behavior of a trusted person in our model

    A Confidence instance is characterized by the following :

    • An id (for the database)
    • An email list (his+the email of his trusted persons)
    • An account name
    • A password
    • A name
    • An address
    • An email address
    • A subscription date
    • A list of trusted persons
    • A boat
    Author:
    Quentin Ducasse
